title: Samsung Galaxy S5 Neo Launches in Brazil as Galaxy S5 New Edition
text: This summer, Samsung quietly introduced the Galaxy S5 Neo smartphone which went on sale in the Netherlands initially. The phone resembles last year’s Galaxy S5 when it comes to dimensions, but its specs have been watered down to make the Galaxy S5 Neo a more affordable, mid-range affair. Now, the phone has been re-branded and launched as the Galaxy S5 New Edition »
